title: Is ‘6MWE’ an Anti-Semitic Proud Boys Slogan?
subtitle: A Proud Boy wearing a shirt with the initialism "6MWE" combined with a fascist symbol was seen in D.C. protesting the election of Joe Biden.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: "6MWE" stands for "6 million wasn't enough" —  a reference to the 6 million Jews murdered during the Holocaust.
